metadata.name: TR-808 #1
metadata.description: The legendary Roland TR-808 has been used on more hit records than any other drum machine in history. Artists like Beyonce, Missy Elliot, Talking Heads, Jay-Z, Aphex Twin, Marvin Gaye, Whitney Houston, Nine Inch Nails, Kanye West, 2Pac, Usher, SOS band plus many more artists have all used the TR-808 Drum Machine to express themselves through their records. Roland Lifestyle is bringing music lovers from around the world a chance to own a piece of this cultural icon by purchasing a TR-808 Digital Collectible.
